name: beautiful flower girl
description:
Flowers are not only beautiful and pleasing to the eye. The fragrant aroma also makes many people like flowers. But yeah, everyone has their own favorite flower. There are those who like jasmine flowers, roses, orchids, tulips and other flowers.
Women who like flowers are generally independent women, love beauty and beauty. Women who love roses are also known as friendly, patient and accepting women. Even so, they are very impressive women because they can always be themselves no matter where she is.
